OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start it will be
OL,6,Fanother dry and bright day and feeling
OL,7,Fa bit milder again. Plenty of sunshine
OL,8,Fon offer, which may turn a bit hazy at
OL,9,Ftimes in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with patchy
OL,12,Fcloud and largely clear skies.
OL,13,FRemaining dry with clear spells
OL,14,Fovernight, leading to a touch of frost
OL,15,Fin rural spots in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
