OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry morning with sunny spells.
OL,6,FRemaining mostly dry through the
OL,7,Fafternoon and turning cloudier, but
OL,8,Fstill some bright or sunny intervals
OL,9,Fbreaking through. Outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fpossible over western Argyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy on Monday with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain. Dry start Tuesday but becoming
OL,15,Fwindier as rain spreads east later.
OL,16,FWindy on Wednesday as rain clears to
OL,17,Fsunny spells and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
